solution
========

Install vite
------------
``npm install -g vite``

Create the project
------------------
``npm create vite@latest``

Install dependencies
--------------------
``npm install``
``npm run dev``

Github pages configuration
--------------------------
Install the gh-pages package
``npm install gh-pages``

In your vite.config.js file include the base tag with the name of your repository
base: '/example'

In your package.json file include the tag homepage with the url of your repository
	"homepage": "https://<username>.github.io/<repository>"

In your package.json include the two scripts
	"predeploy": "npm run build",
	"deploy": "gh-pages -d dist"

Deploy
------
npm run deploy
